    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701880/extras/9ad342255fe90c78b0c8e396cd779c0d.poster.avif?t=1705489054\" width=384 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701880/extras/9ad342255fe90c78b0c8e396cd779c0d.webm?t=1705489054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701880/extras/9ad342255fe90c78b0c8e396cd779c0d.mp4?t=1705489054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Welcome to <strong>Chaos Brigade Demo</strong>!<br><br>Lead a team of fearless space exterminators, in their quest to cleanse the galaxy from the filth of evil aliens races. <br><br>In this <strong>retro-arcade-platform-shooter</strong> you will assault drifting spaceships, wipe out the invaders and claim your reward. <br><br>But be careful! Your weapons can damage the spaceship you are meant to save and can ultimately cause its destruction!<br><br><i>Kill the aliens, save the spaceship, earn Bitcoins!</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701880/extras/8d0b978acf09c68ecd8f278637cea5ef.avif?t=1705489054\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701880/extras_big/8d0b978acf09c68ecd8f278637cea5ef.avif?t=1705489054 width=800 height=162 /></span><br><br>In this DEMO you will experience bits of the complete game:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2 out of 6 exterminators available! You can control the leader of the Brigade: Dr. Paradox himself! Or, if you prefer sheer power, you can play with Private Jane.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A sample of the threats you will face at the beginning of your adventure: the Infestoid worm-like aliens and the flickering Rimwalkers!</li></ul><br>If you like the Demo, please add <strong>Chaos Brigade</strong> to your Wishlist! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701880/extras/8d0b978acf09c68ecd8f278637cea5ef.avif?t=1705489054\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701880/extras_big/8d0b978acf09c68ecd8f278637cea5ef.avif?t=1705489054 width=800 height=162 /></span>",
